data.description: Welcome to the Johnson Ranch lifestyle! This 4-bedroom single-story home is the epitome of convenience and comfort. Step inside to find a spacious living or play area and a well-equipped kitchen with granite counters and rich wood cabinets, seamlessly connected to the family room. Two bedrooms are centrally located, while the master suite and another bedroom reside at the rear of the house, ensuring privacy. A 'walk-through' bathroom adds to the practicality. Enjoy the upgraded master bath with a new vanity and tub/shower enclosure. Owned Solar, Tank-less water heater, wood floors, whole house water softener, and a complete wireless security system all contribute to make this a fantastic deal!
